text: Garhi Ismail Zai is a town and Union Council of Mardan District in the Khyber Pakhtunkhwa province of Pakistan. It is located at 34°12'0N 72°10'0E and has a height of 294 metres (967 feet).Location of Garhi Ismailzai - Falling Rain Genomics ==References== Category:Union councils of Mardan District
